'''Rim Riders' Travel Associates''' was a travel agency that provided trips on middle-market [[Luxury liner/Legends|luxury liners]] to the [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid]] and [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim Territories]] for inhabitants of the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core Worlds]].

